             was indicted for <rs id="t17910112-36-off189" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910112-36-off189" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910112-36-off189" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17910112-36-cd190" type="crimeDate">11th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910112-36-off189 t17910112-36-cd190"></join>, two pewter pint pots, value 16 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17910112-36-victim407" type="victimName">
                     Lewis 
                     Rotely
                  <interp inst="t17910112-36-victim407" type="surname" value="Rotely"></interp>
