                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910112-36-defend405 t17910112-36-punish193"></join>
               Publicly whipped
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17910112-36-punish194" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910112-36-punish194" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910112-36-punish194" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="newgate"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910112-36-defend405 t17910112-36-punish194"></join>
               three months imprisonment in Newgate
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
